data.description: Captivating opportunity to own a spacious 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom condo in the desirable community of Kendall Acres West Condominium. Features brand-new stainless-steel appliances, in unit washer/dryer and new tile throughout. Open bright living/dining rooms. Master suite with full bathroom and walk in closet. Enjoy stunning views of the pool/tennis courts from your screened balcony. One assigned parking and ample guest parking in a well-maintained Community offering security patrol and amenities such as clubhouse, pool, gym, pool tables, tennis courts, and car wash area. Prime location near shopping plazas, dining options, Baptist Hospital, parks, prestigious universities, supermarkets nearby and convenient access to FL-Turnpike, Don Shula Expressway (FL-874), and Palmetto Expressway.
